@*1 auxg. 
Find the maximum value of $F_\nu$ required, use |fmch| to
compute it and obtain all the lower $F_\nu$ by downward recursion.
$$
F_{\nu-1}(x) = {{\exp(-x) + 2 x F_\nu (x) } \over {2 \nu -1 }}
